vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 42A, “Special Events; Neighborhood Markets; Dallas Street Seats; Dallas Farmers Market Farmers Market; Streetlight Pole Banners,” of the Dallas City Code by amending Section 42A-12 for the purpose of providing an extension of the temporary parklet program provisions until September 30, 2021 - Financing: No cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
